'''Anand''' ({{lang-gu|આણંદ}}, {{IPA2|äɽ̃ən̪d̪}}) is the administrative centre of [[Anand District]] in the state of [[Gujarat]], [[India]]. It is administered by Anand Municipality. It is part of the region known as '''Charotar''' comprising of Anand & Kheda Districts.
Ing '''Anand''' ({{lang-gu|આણંદ}}, {{IPA2|äɽ̃ən̪d̪}}) ing sentru ning pamanibala ning [[Anand District]] king estadu ning [[Gujarat]], [[India]]. Palakad ne ning Anand Municipality. Kayabe ya king labuad (''region'') a ausan dang '''Charotar''', a bibilugan da reng distritu ning Anand ampong Kheda.

